  "special": {
    "title": "Love is a Lady Finger. True love is a Lady Fist.",
    "description": "Greatly increases critical-hit damage in exchange for lower base gun damage. It also boosts projectile speed and magazine size, while keeping Hyperion's improving accuracy during sustained fire."
  },
  "notes": "Its reduced base damage and massive crit bonus create an enormous gap between critical and non-critical damage. The bonus is multiplicative, so extra crit boosts add less than you might expect on top of it. During Gunzerking, both guns' crit bonuses apply, letting Salvador stack absurd critical-hit damage with another crit-focused weapon. The bonus can also carry over to some slow projectiles if you swap to it before impact, and it can affect vehicle primary weapons and the Outrunner turret if it is equipped when you enter.",
